oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Thomas Paton "Tuck" Strawn's (1850-1918) house, Hillsboro. The people are: Elmer Anderson Strawn (1875-1960); Jarrett Brandon Strawn (1874-1954); Jarrett's wife Myrtle Hattie Ferguson Strawn (1877-1969); Argie Leola Strawn (1903-1905) ; Orion Dale Strawn (1900-1995); Miss Jimmy Strawn; Mrs. Catherine Gentry Strawn.
